headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Exotic Exports
content: Is there any thrill bigger than purchasing a brand-new car? Well, it’s a close-run thing, but how about stealing it and selling it on? Auto Shop owners who have completed a Contract should check the chalkboard for their daily list of wanted vehicles. Find and deliver them to the docks for a reward. Deliver them all and you’ll receive a bonus. Can’t say fairer than that. Unless you’re the one being jacked…
